WEBVTT

00:09:59.720 --> 00:10:02.376
until he had taken a shower
and changed his clothes.

00:10:02.400 --> 00:10:06.736
So he physically wanted
to detach from work

00:10:06.760 --> 00:10:11.200
before he felt like he was
literally clean to enter the home.

00:10:12.280 --> 00:10:14.576
AG: Was that just a germ thing

00:10:14.600 --> 00:10:17.016
or was there something
also more symbolic about it?

00:10:17.040 --> 00:10:18.936
NR: No, it was not a germ thing at all.

00:10:18.960 --> 00:10:20.496
It was totally symbolic.

00:10:20.520 --> 00:10:25.816
So it was a completely
symbolic recognition

00:10:25.840 --> 00:10:27.320
that he was shedding ...